Pendulum Effect
 Once per turn: You can target 1 "DD" monster you control; its Level becomes 4, and if it does, it gains 400 ATK and DEF.

 Monster Effect
 When this card is Pendulum Summoned from your hand while you control a "DD" monster, except "DD Cerberus": You can target 1 Continuous Spell Card in your Graveyard; add it to your hand.
